{"title":"炉前放歌","authors":["何玉锁"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":6,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉前放歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京工人　何玉锁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟声，当！当！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红光，飞升！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲天炉熔炼着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤红的铁水！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们胸中激荡着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的豪情！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥热汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站炉前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披金戴红！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"持钢钎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼望万里前程！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国江山亲手铸牢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜驾驭着时代的东风！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰隆隆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉口打开——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁水俯冲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈火熊熊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像铁水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像烈火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧！飞腾！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞上昆仑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞向万里平原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热气腾腾！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员们欢呼——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新式农具握手中！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！社员的汗水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！我们的汗水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一起交融！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作春风春雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"润出一片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的收成！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耳边春雷滚滚——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖拉机、新机床……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔出工厂——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向天南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向海北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运行！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷声呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我们的心声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在轰鸣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将把历史的巨轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推向新的里程！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的心呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧！飞腾！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞遍祖国千山万水——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处红光闪闪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望尽万里云天——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"片片红光飞升！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类理想的黎明！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看！红光越升越高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的象征！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}